ports for a variety of publications  Best Regrets will be available for purchase after October 20th at the VMI bookstore  540 464 7637  and the VMI Museum  540 464 7334  via phone or in person  You can also purchase a signed copy at the football game against Furman on November 1st  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI   OUR MISSION  To contribute to the Spirit and development of a successful Division I Athletic Program  that benefits the WHOLE OF VMI  THE VMI KEYDET CLUB Neikirk Hall   304 Letcher Avenue P O  Box 932   Lexington  VA 24450 P  800 444 1839    P  540 464 7328    F  540 463 2695  2014 VMI   Lexington  Virginia 24450 Privacy Policy   Webmaster 